<p><img height="225" width="300" src="http://www.edenhrconsulting.com/images/stories/eden-stick-figures/eden-rules-regulations.jpg" alt="eden-rules-regulations" style="float: right;" />Sometimes no matter what we do, we will be faced with an unexpected issue and you will need to know where you stand legally.</p>
<p>Whether it’s a grievance, disciplinary, long-term sick cases or receipt of an Employment Tribunal claim (ET1), we can help. Call us and we will advise you on the legal aspects, give advice on the issue at hand, discuss your options and then act as necessary.</p>
<p>In terms of rules and regulations, our services revolve primarily around best practice and employment law advice and implementing the recommendations we put forward. We also create the foundation documentation such as contracts of employment, policies and procedures and employee handbooks/ manuals.</p></td>
